<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Meu Blog</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        nav {
            background-color: #444;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 15px;
        }

        section {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }

        form {
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        input[type="submit"] {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Meu Blog</h1>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <a href="/index">Home</a>
        <a href="/sobre">Sobre</a>
        <a href="/contatos">Contatos</a>
        <a href="/login">Postagens</a>
    </nav>

    <section>
        <!-- Conteúdo da página vai aqui -->
        <h2>Bem-vindo ao Meu Blog!</h2>
        <p>Este é um blog incrível com conteúdo interessante.</p>
    </section>

    <footer>
        &copy; 2024 Meu Blog. Todos os direitos reservados.
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
